{"article_id":"rEQD8UOl83KCjrrz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"On Tuesday , Senate Republicans moved closer to handing President Donald Trump an impeachment trial","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"without witnesses , evidence , or documents .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Such a trial will likely result in the acquittal or the dismissal of charges","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that the president desperately craves .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"After passing charges of abuse of power and obstruction of Congress ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"then holding them back from the Senate for three weeks in the name","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"of preventing such a sham trial ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Democrats now themselves appear ready to go along with the Republican plan .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"First , Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell told reporters on Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that he has the votes","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"he needs","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"to proceed to his desired Senate trial format ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"in which any vote on witnesses would be delayed","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"until after the cases had been presented .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"As Minority Leader Chuck Schumer has previously noted ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"this is a simple ruse .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"McConnell has already promised to follow up the initial argument phase of the trial","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"by holding a vote","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"to end it ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"before any new witnesses or documents can be brought to light through subpoenas .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"McConnell , that is , has pledged to prevent the public from hearing testimony under oath from crucial witnesses like former national security adviser John Bolton ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"who on Monday offered to testify","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"and who has said","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"he has information directly relevant to the charges","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"that the president blocked security aid to Ukraine","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"to pressure that nation ' s leadership to announce an investigation of Joe Biden .","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"As Schumer has noted ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"holding a trial without witnesses would amount to replaying the House impeachment hearings ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"rather than actually trying the case against the president .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"\" It is not the Senate ' s job to put the House impeachment proceedings on a weeklong rerun on C-SPAN , \"","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"As Schumer further noted in a floor speech on Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Bill Clinton ' s impeachment trial had witness depositions in the Senate ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"and Andrew Johnson ' s impeachment trial had 41 witnesses .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"\" A trial isn ' t a trial","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"without evidence .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"A trial","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"without all the facts","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"is a farce , \"","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Schumer argued .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" If the president is ultimately acquitted at the end of a sham trial ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"his acquittal will be meaningless. \"","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Speaker of the House Nancy Pelosi had promised to withhold the articles of impeachment","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"until Senate leadership offered a clearer picture","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"of what that trial would look like ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"as a strategy","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"to try to prevent Republicans from rigging the proceedings","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"to protect Trump .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"And now ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"having established the central importance","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"of having a real trial with witnesses ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"the Democrats are apparently ready to give up","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"and let McConnell run things his way .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"the speaker should send the articles","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"regardless [ of whether there will be witnesses ] , \"","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Sen. Chris Murphy told reporters on Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"the time has passed .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"She should send the articles over . \"","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"On Tuesday afternoon , Schumer all but confirmed","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"that this phase of impeachment had ended .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"\" The speaker has said all along","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"that she wanted to see the arena","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"in which she was playing","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"when it came to a trial","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"so that she could appoint impeachment managers , \"","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"\" Now it ' s becoming clear that Mitch McConnell wants to do everything","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"he can","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"to avoid a fair trial ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"so she has some idea of what ' s happened . \"","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"The New York Democrat further argued","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"that Pelosi ' s temporary delay tactics had \" helped our case \"","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"even if it was time","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"to move on .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"McConnell , meanwhile , was making it clear exactly how that trial would go ,","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"telling reporters","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"he had the votes","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"to block witnesses in the first phase , with potential swing Sens . Susan Collins , Lisa Murkowski , and Mitt Romney confirming","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that they supported his plan .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Faced with McConnell ' s disciplined strategy","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"to protect Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"it seems ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"the Democrats have decided to give up on the Senate","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"and hope","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"they can win in the court of public opinion .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"\" We have always known","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"that leader McConnell would not be for a fair trial , \"","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Schumer said during the press conference .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"\" He said that from the beginning . \"","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Schumer now says","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"that forcing votes on witnesses at the end of an initial trial presentation might still work to pressure vulnerable senators to come along ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"after having argued for days","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that McConnell ' s plan was a \" poorly disguised trap . \"","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"\" If we leave the question of witnesses and documents","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"until after all the presentations are complete ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"leader McConnell will argue","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"that the Senate has heard enough ,","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"and we shouldn ' t prolong the trial any longer , \"","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"Schumer said last week .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"\" At that point , you can be sure","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"he ' ll label anyone","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"who wants to subpoena evidence","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"as a partisan","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"who wants to drag the whole affair out . \"","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"Now Democrats appear to be barreling full steam ahead into this very trap","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"and hoping","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"that pressure","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"that hasn ' t worked thus far","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"will work at the end of opening presentations .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"\" Many of [ McConnell ' s ] colleagues are very , very worried about going home","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"and saying","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"they are not for witnesses and documents , \"","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"\" They ' re afraid to say yes [ to witnesses ] ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"because they know","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"Donald Trump will be furious at them .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"They ' re afraid to say no","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"because they know","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"their voters ,","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"their constituents will be furious at them .","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"They ' re stuck . \"","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"For the time being , though , they ' ve sided with McConnell .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"There seems to be little reason","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"to believe","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"that will change in the next couple of weeks","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"even if the polling shows","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"the public wants witnesses .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"A FiveThirtyEight/Ipsos impeachment tracking poll","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"released last week","depth":15},{"id":131,"text":"showed","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"that 57 percent of respondents supported witnesses ,","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"confirming previous polls .","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"In the same poll , though , 52 percent of respondents opposed Democrats","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"seeking to delay the trial .","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"So the decision","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"to move ahead under terms","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"dictated by McConnell","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"may have seemed necessary , from a poll-watching standpoint .","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"Still , it ' s impossible not to see it as a capitulation to a defeat in the Senate-one","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"which Trump will tout as a complete exoneration .","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"while the last phase of the impeachment fight was about convincing the public","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"that a trial matters ,","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"and that it ought to include witnesses ,","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"the next phase will be about trying to convince the public to hold Republicans accountable","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"where the Democrats could not .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"Democrats think","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"they can make the case","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"that potentially vulnerable senators like Collins , Colorado ' s Cory Gardner , North Carolina ' s Thom Tillis , and Arizona ' s Martha McSally have shirked their duty .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"A Senate Democratic aide pointed to fresh surveys from a Democratic pollster","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"that indicated","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"that these four at least would be viewed unfavorably in their home states","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"if they blocked witnesses and documents .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"But that polling took place in a context","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"where Democrats were actively fighting for impeachment ,","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"rather than yielding to McConnell themselves .","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"On Monday we got the first taste of what Democratic efforts","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"to target these senators","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"might look like with the release of a super PAC ad in Arizona","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"going after McSally .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"The campaign portrayed McSally","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"wearing a golden arches fast food franchise branded uniform","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"labeled \" McSally ' s. \"","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"It accused her of flip-flopping","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"( like a burger ! )","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"on Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals and of being dismissive of the Ukraine scandal .","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"The ad leaned heavily into soft drink imagery ,","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"showing a cartoon cutout of a fast food uniformed McSally","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"selling \" souvenir cups \"","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"featuring a previous quote of the senator ' s","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"calling the Ukraine investigation a \" kamikaze mission \" for Democrats .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"The idea is that the voters should keep holding that against her ,","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"even after the Democrats let the impeachment trial crash and burn .","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"Update , Jan. 8 , 2020 , at 12:10 p.m. :","depth":3},{"id":176,"text":"On Tuesday evening , Pelosi sent out a \" Dear Colleague \" letter to fellow members of the House","depth":5},{"id":177,"text":"indicating","depth":6},{"id":178,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"before transmitting articles of impeachment to the Senate ,","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"she wanted to see the specific resolution","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"McConnell was proposing .","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"\" It is important that he immediately publish this resolution ,","depth":5},{"id":183,"text":"so that ,","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"as I have said before ,","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"we can see the arena","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"in which we will be participating ,","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"appoint managers","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"and transmit the articles to the Senate , \"","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":6},{"id":190,"text":"McConnell has said consistently","depth":4},{"id":191,"text":"that he ' d like to use the 1999 Bill Clinton impeachment resolution as a template","depth":4},{"id":192,"text":"and said on Tuesday ,","depth":4},{"id":193,"text":"\" We ' ll be glad to show [ the resolution ] to you","depth":5},{"id":194,"text":"when we unveil it . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":389,"left":369,"right":388,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":369,"left":236,"right":368,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":198,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":196,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":201,"right":234,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":200,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":200,"left":4,"right":199,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":223,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":208,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":206,"right":207,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":8,"right":205,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":205,"left":203,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":202,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":222,"left":217,"right":221,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":211,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":16,"right":210,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":209,"right":19,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"paren